[0-23] "Fear is the mind-killer." fg=#e0e0e0 bg=#800080
[24-119] "                                                                                                " fg=def bg=#800080
--row 1--
[0-55] "Fear is the little-death that brings total obliteration." fg=#e0e0e0 bg=#800080
[56-119] "                                                                " fg=def bg=#800080
--row 2--
[0-19] "I will face my fear." fg=#e0e0e0 bg=#800080
[20-119] "                                                                                                    " fg=def bg=#800080
--row 3--
[0-47] "I will permit it to pass over me and through me." fg=#e0e0e0 bg=#800080
[48-119] "                                                                        " fg=def bg=#800080
--row 4--
[0-68] "And when it has gone past, I will turn the inner eye to see its path." fg=#e0e0e0 bg=#800080
[69-119] "                                                   " fg=def bg=#800080
--row 5--
[0-65] "Where the fear has gone there will be nothing. Only I will remain." fg=#e0e0e0 bg=#800080
